question: Model sing endi sing nyedhiyakake scalability Sublinear, lan apa bedane fitur sing didhukung ('Pre-training', 'Multi-task')?
answer: TimeMixer lan PatchTST nyedhiyakake scalability Sublinear. Bedane yaiku TimeMixer ndhukung Multi-task learning dene PatchTST ora; loro model kasebut ora nggunakake Pre-training.

question: Pira cacahe model sing nyengkuyung Pre-training utawa Multi-task learning, nanging ora loro-lorone?
Sebutna aplikasi utama model sing duwe scalability Linear lan kebutuhan compute Medium.
Nek proyek riset berkembang saka mbutuhake model kanggo 'Long Sequences' banjur butuh sing duwe 'Task Flexibility', model endi sing cocog kanggo pilihan ing tahap kapindho?
Sebutna model-model sing ora nganggo pre-training lan nyediakake scalability sublinear.
Pira persentase model sing kasebut mbutuhake sumber daya komputasi 'High'?
Nek 'TimesNet' ditambah ben iso 'Pre-training', model sing wis ana endi sing paling cedhak karo fitur-fiture (Pre-training, Multi-task, Compute, Scalability)?
answer: TimesNet sing wis ditambah kuwi ora bakal cedhak karo model liyane. Senajan bakal padha 'Pre-training', 'Multi-task', lan 'Linear' scalability karo Timer lan MOMENT, nanging 'Medium' compute-ne isih bakal beda karo 'High' compute-ne.

question: Ono sesambungan sing katon antarane kemampuan model kanggo nyelarasake lan fokus utama aplikasine ing dawa urutan utawa fleksibilitas?
answer: Ya, katone ana sesambungan. Model kanthi kemampuan nyelarasake 'Sublinear' sing luwih efisien (TimeMixer, PatchTST) ana gandheng cenenge karo aplikasi sing nglibatake pola kompleks utawa urutan dawa ('Multiscale Patterns', 'Long Sequences'). Kosok baline, model kanthi kemampuan nyelarasake 'Linear' cenderung digunakake kanggo tugas sing mbutuhake fleksibilitas utawa sinau ing sangisore watesan ('Few-shot Learning', 'Limited Supervision', 'Task Flexibility').
